          <p class="vcard">&#169; <span class="fn org">Stanford University</span>, <span class="adr"><span class="locality">Stanford</span>, <span class="region">California</span> <span class="postal-code">94305</span></span>. <span class="copyright-links"><a href="http://www.stanford.edu/site/copyright.html">Copyright Complaints</a></span></p>
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
